{"tid":967243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「龍心」涉咬傷保安　女友圖阻警拘捕　二人拒認罪准保釋","createTime":"2019-01-03T10:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T15:46:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c7222dda516765f884a06daa45d21ae668e38f93","tid":967243,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"自稱為網絡紅人的「龍心」林克霖，前年在西九龍文化區咬傷一名外籍保安，警員到場拘捕他時，其女友鄭芷琪上前試圖阻止。「龍心」被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，鄭則被控抗拒警務人員罪，兩人今於九龍城裁判法院一同不認罪，排期至2月21日開審。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指，林克霖（41歲）於去年9月30日，在香港西九龍文化區苗圃公園內襲擊Paul Salter。鄭芷琪（19歲）則被指於上述地點，抗拒警員楊仲明。控方透露，僅會傳召受傷保安作供，二人沒有錄影會面紀錄，預計審期1天。裁判官准二人繼續保釋。"},{"pid":"6393d066fd410051ab56a6b4204fb237cc7e49e5","tid":967243,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:55:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190103/s00001/1546508484128/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190103%2Fs00001%2F1546508484128%2F&d=e6R0DSEO%2BDOF4QK4gxIeYJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0cdc7cec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190103%2Fs00001%2F1546508484128%2F&h=d847fa7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190103/s00001/1546508484128/</a>"},{"pid":"dc2a86a8fef3a3f96fb4c1cd244c2594157a64e2","tid":967243,"uid":156133,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T10:59:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>自稱為網絡紅人的「龍心」林克霖</strong><br />\n<br />\n自稱為「龍心」的網絡紅人林克霖？"},{"pid":"f41cd1e8877cbe780cb3df2d86e3a54fb137d315","tid":967243,"uid":12034,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"前年在西九龍文化區咬傷一名外籍保安<br />\n<br />\n去年9月30日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"df605692074a0c05a5a865b96a52fd59f9c48f93","tid":967243,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"reply